    "description": {
      "zh": "MDT ESS底盘系统引入了诸多创新特性，这些设计理念持续影响着MDT后续底盘产品的开发方向，例如采用M-LOK护木、双侧弹匣释放钮，以及XTN枪托接口设计——该接口为握持手预留了自然摆放空间。",
      "en": "The MDT ESS Chassis System introduced a lot of features that have since driven design decisions on MDT chassis moving forward, such as the M-LOK forend, ambidextrous magazine latch, and the XTN buttstock interface that allows room for your hand to sit naturally."
